title: 이달의소녀탐구 #467 (LOONA TV #467)
summary:
Woo! New Era!!
0:07 -- Go Won and Hye recollect that it has been a while since they were at the airport.
0:16 -- Go Won and Hye: "Happy new year~"
0:22 -- They are the only two members at the airport at that time since (accroding to Go Won) "[they] are most special members~"
0:26 -- Olivia Hye starts to 'Hmm' and chooses her words carefully.
0:32 - Go Won: "My face looks stupid today..."
0:37 -- Hye talks about they both are the members most sensitive to cold and are going to Iceland. They will have to share the pain that HaSeul had to go through before.
0:53 -- The two arrive in Iceland and they are freezing.
